“Banan” so‘zining 20 ta belgidan iborat, o‘ngga asoslangan versiyasini qaytaring:

txt = "banana"

x = txt.rjust(20)

print(x, "is my favorite fruit.")

Eslatma: Natijada, banan so'zining chap tomonida 14 ta bo'sh joy mavjud.

Ta'rifi va qo'llanilishi
Usul rjust()to'ldirish belgisi sifatida belgilangan belgidan (bo'sh joy sukut bo'yicha) foydalanib, satrni to'g'ri tekislaydi.

Sintaksis
string.rjust(length, character)

Parametr qiymatlari
Parameter	Description
length	---- Required. The length of the returned string
character ----	Optional. A character to fill the missing space (to the left of the string). Default is " " (space).
